-- Luxottica, Coach Announce Licensing Agreement for Eyewear Starting in 2012
-- B y   D a n   L i e f g r e e n
-- 2010-10-05T09:01:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/luxottica-coach-announce-licensing-agreement-for-eyewear-starting-in-2012.html
Luxottica Group SpA and Coach Inc.
signed a licensing agreement for the design, manufacturing and
global distribution of sun and prescription eyewear under the
Coach, Coach Poppy and Reed Krakoff brands, the companies said
in a statement. The partnership starts in January 2012.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Liefgreen at 
 dliefgreen@bloomberg.net  